front.title: •Ak-rev
front.gametext: Subtracts 1 from attrition against you at same site. Once during each of your control phases, may use 1 Force to take one musician into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.
front.lore: Weequay musician from Sriluur. Studied in a monastery devoted to the Weequay god of thunder. Jabba's drum master. Trained in several forms of hand-to-hand combat.
